    <p>Zelda3 is a reverse engineered clone of Zelda - A Link to the Past.</p>
    <p>A bunch of features have been added that are not supported by the original game.</p>
    <p>Due to the legality an original US region ROM (SHA1: 66871d66be19ad2c34c927d6b14cd8eb6fc3181965b6e517cb361f7316009cfb) is required to play.</p>
    <p>In addition, translations can be added through localized ROMs.</p>
